step.context:
\text{Does the shaded region in this plot}\\
\text{correctly represent the feasible region,} \\
\text{given the constraints?}

step.reason:
\text{Line constraint }y\ge mx+c \text{ means feasible }\\
\text{region is above the lines. The line with the}\\
\text{greater y for the same x forms the bottom}

\text{Open half plane created by }3x+5y\lt 7 \text{ is}\\
\text{below it, so no overlap. The minimum}\\
\text{therefore is 7 at (1.5, 0.5)}
